Spacious, over half an acre outside the city limits. Updated two bedroom/2.5 bath with addition flex room.  Principal bedroom with en suite bath and secondary bedroom with half bath.  Seller has made extensive upgrades to the crawlspace.  Seller is offering a home warranty.
